description:
Eddie Daniels recently visited Morrie Backun and the staff at Backun Musical Services to have his clarinets tuned and voiced. While in the shop, Eddie took some time to share his thoughts on the art of noodling and playing the clarinet. 

This is the first video of many that BMS is posting as part of its new social media program. To learn more about Backun products and the artists who play them: visit our website, find us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter:
